WEBVTT

00:02.001 --> 00:03.629
<i>Previously, on</i> One Tree Hill...

00:03.703 --> 00:06.934
I've got a way for you to leave,
but you've got to go in the morning.

00:07.007 --> 00:08.406
-Hey.
-What's wrong?

00:08.475 --> 00:10.841
You know how much
I care about you, Anna...

00:12.445 --> 00:13.912
but there's somebody else.

00:15.448 --> 00:17.211
Is this what you're after?

00:22.088 --> 00:23.077
Jake.

00:23.857 --> 00:24.983
I lied to you.

00:26.893 --> 00:28.155
I slept with Keith.

00:28.428 --> 00:29.759
Hey, Jules. It's Keith.

00:29.829 --> 00:32.161
<i>I just realized something</i>
<i>and I had to say it.</i>

00:32.465 --> 00:34.456
I love you.

00:34.534 --> 00:37.401
Nice work, Jules. Just like we planned.

00:37.604 --> 00:40.471
Haley, you owe it to your music.
You owe it to yourself.

00:40.707 --> 00:42.436
Your dreams are a bus ride away.

00:42.776 --> 00:44.073
<i>I know it's scary.</i>

00:44.144 --> 00:46.476
But just tell me
if you can show me your heart.

00:46.546 --> 00:49.071
If you do, I'll guard it with my life.

